album.title: Best of Ella Fitzgerald & Louis Armstrong

track.name: They Can't Take That Away From Me
comments: Spending the day listening to Ella and Louis.  Life is good.
i am so happy today welcome back to my time!!!!!
oh oh  i can't talk this take my breath away!!!!!
louie's timing is beyong the beyond! He laid his 1st vocal note in soooo on. Ella's return was as if she was stipping on a pair of stockings
This is the best thing ever. Period.
the way you haunt my dreams...
I'll always, always keep the memory of...Louie and Ella!
The Duchess and Pops--it just doesn't get any better than this.  Two of the ultimate jazz voices and the greatest jazz trumpet player of all time.  Their every duet is classic.
One of the great songs ...great duo singing and playing it.
is this the most perfect combo ever???? I can't stop swinging...........you can't take this away from me.they are perfect
